data.text: This is starting period of Shani's Sade Sati. In this period Saturn will be transiting in 12th house from the Moon. It generally indicates financial loss, problems by hidden enemies, aimless travel, disputes, and poverty. During this period, Mahesh Bhupathi may face problems created by Mahesh Bhupathi's hidden enemies. Relationship with Mahesh Bhupathi's colleagues will not good enough and they will create problems in Mahesh Bhupathi's work environment. Mahesh Bhupathi may also face challenges on Mahesh Bhupathi's domestic front. This may create pressure and tension. Mahesh Bhupathi need to exercise control over Mahesh Bhupathi's spending otherwise it be lead to bigger financial problems. Long distance travels may not be fruitful during this period. Saturn's nature is of delay and dejection, but generally Mahesh Bhupathi will get results eventually, so be patient and wait for Mahesh Bhupathi's turn. Take this period as learning period, put Mahesh Bhupathi's hard work and things will fall in place. Mahesh Bhupathi advised not to take high risks in business matters in this period. This is the peak of Shani's Sade Sati. Generally this phase of Saturn is the most difficult one. Saturn transiting over natal Moon indicates health problems, character assassination, problems in relationship, mental afflictions, and sorrows. Mahesh Bhupathi will find it difficult to achieve success in this period. Mahesh Bhupathi may not get results of Mahesh Bhupathi's hard work and feel restricted. Mahesh Bhupathi's constitution and immune system will not be strong. As first house is the house of health, Mahesh Bhupathi should start exercising and taking care of Mahesh Bhupathi's health, otherwise Mahesh Bhupathi can be caught by chronic diseases. Mahesh Bhupathi may suffer from depression, unknown fear or phobia. Mahesh Bhupathi's will lack clarity in thinking, action, and decision making. Mahesh Bhupathi will be spiritually inclined and will be attracted by intricacies of nature. Acceptance and doing basics right will sail Mahesh Bhupathi out of this period.
